engineCMS::dbTables()

Description
    public mixed engineCMS::dbTables(string $action [, string $state = "prod" [, string $value = NULL]])
    Adds elements to the internal dbTables array.

Parameters
    action
	
    state
	Optional parameter with the DB's status.  Default value is "prod."
    value
	Optional parameter.  Default value is NULL.

Return Values
    TRUE, FALSE or the value stored in $this->dbTables[$action][$state]

Examples

    <?php
	...
	$engine->dbTables("accessPlainText", "prod", "accessPlainText");
	...
    ?>

Notes
   
See Also
